SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast (sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO - CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN - CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO) as decimal(13,2)), (cast (sum (CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALCREDNOTESAUTO) as decimal(13,2)) / cast (sum (CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESMAN + CMON_TOTSALDEBTNOTESAUTO) as decimal(13,2)))* 100, cast (sum (CMON_TOTIIFACTDEBIT + CMON_TOTIIFACTSURCHARGEOD + CMON_TOTIIARRANGEM + CMON_TOTIISTOCK) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHED + CMON_TOTIFACTCOMMSCHEDADD + CMON_TOTIMINCOMM + CMON_TOTIFIXCOMM + CMON_TOTICOMMCREDITNOTES) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTIINSURANCECOMM) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTOTHERINCOME) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTIIFACTCREDIT) as decimal(13,2)), cast (sum (CMON_TOTIICREDCOMM + CMON_TOTIIARRANGEMCREDCOMM + CMON_TOTIISTOCKCREDITCOMM) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5'

select cast (avg (CMON_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFROINVDAT / CMON_TOTAPAIDINV) as decimal(13,2)), cast (avg (CMON_OUTINVAVGDAYSINV) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/CMON where CMON_ADMNO = :2 and CMON_CLNTNO = :3 and CMON_YEAR = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ':5'
select cast (sum (CDEP_ACTUALAMOUNTHELL) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/CDEP where CDEP_ADMNO = :2 and CDEP_CLNTNO = :3 and CDEP_TYPE :4 and CDEP_DATEDELETED is null
